content:
Firely invites healthtech startups to attend HL7 FHIR DevDays and compete in the Startup Track for a cash prize of $2500. Please share with any people or startups you know who might be interested!
For more information and registration please visit: https://www.devdays.com/november-2020/startup-track/
Any chance of maybe clarifying which time exactly the sessions are? On the schedule it is slightly confusing - but then again it might be my Kiwi mind..;) image.png Thank you
Discussion and questions, please on https://chat.fhir.org/#narrow/stream/242116-DevDays-Support , not on this channel.
Thanks for highlighting my mistake..and sorry about it..actually got the response form the Orgnaisers via email already. Would have like to remove my comment but unfortunately not possible.
